# MoveEquipmentAction.Order.atIndex(_:)

**Case**

Inserts the equipment at a specific location Note: the equipment is inserted at a undefined location if the index provided is not valid

## Declaration

```swift
case atIndex(Int)
```

## Orders

- **MoveEquipmentAction.Order.first**: Inserts the equipment at the beginning of the list
- **MoveEquipmentAction.Order.last**: Inserts the equipment at the end of the list
- **MoveEquipmentAction.Order.before(_:)**: Inserts the equipment before the specified equipment identifier.
- **MoveEquipmentAction.Order.after(_:)**: Inserts the equipment after the specified equipment identifier.
